description:
Speaker: Jeremy Tuloup

Track:PyData
JupyterLab can be extended via third-party extensions written by developers from the Jupyter community.

This is a tour of 20 of these extensions, in 20 minutes. Demos included!

Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2019 conference.
https://pycon.de

More details at the conference page: https://de.pycon.org/program/EH7FWD
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/pydataberlin
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/pyconde
title: A Tour of JupyterLab Extensions
